title: Jenkins and Jonez - Comedy Is Dead But the MVP Race Is Alive
itunes:title: Jenkins and Jonez - Comedy Is Dead But the MVP Race Is Alive
description:
The guys discuss the enduring comedy of the Will Smith/Chris Rock incident, the impending doom that is Duke beating UNC, the nuances of the NBA MVP race, the Lakers dropping out of the playoffs, and the latest with ‘Winning Time’.
